Class ConnectionPipe

java.lang.Object
  client.connectionPipe.ConnectionPipe

public class ConnectionPipe
extends java.lang.Object

Author:
marc This gstreamer pipe connects to the given server and informs all connected listeners by pipeline changes. The pipeline has to be initialized init() and then set to run run()
